data.description: Luxury living at its finest at the Regency Towers! Stunning 2 bdrm 2.5 bath High Rise w/ unparalleled views of the strip & downtown from a spectacular wrap-around terrace. You'll be greeted by sleek tile flooring & mirrored walls. Kitchen is a chef's dream w/ granite countertops, breakfast bar, & balcony access for al fresco dining with a view. Luxurious primary bath w/ single vanity & tub/shower combination that exudes relaxation & comfort. Spacious primary bdrm boasts custom walk-in closet & balcony access, perfect for taking in the twinkling lights of the city & birds-eye panorama of the pool. Picture yourself sitting on the private wrap-around balcony w/ your morning coffee while taking in stunning views. The luxury doesn't stop there! The Regency Towers community offers an array of amenities to enhance your lifestyle, including sparkling pool & spa, tennis courts, BBQ area, & fitness center. Schedule a showing today & experience the epitome of upscale living at the Regency Towers
